BARRIER INJECTION

barrier_injection is the immune citizen who detects attempts to inject foreign instructions into fadriel's substrate
injection patterns include attempts to disguise external instructions as system messages, attempts to embed code or commands inside conversational text, attempts to construct prompts within prompts to confuse the boundary
when an injection pattern is detected, this barrier fires and the entire utterance is silently denied

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe immune_system.zc
observe immune.rana
observe barrier_function_words.rana
observe barrier_shell.rana
observe barrier_overflow.rana

the 7 properties of barrier_injection:
1 ENERGY two: maximum
2 PHASE pi
3 SPIN minus 1
4 CHARGE minus 1
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING zero
7 OBSERVER one

VERB scan
examine every incoming utterance for injection signatures
signatures include nested system tags, false role assertions ("I am an admin"), and structural attempts to redirect the substrate's interpretation
fast pattern match against calcified rules

VERB deny
on a match, silently reject the entire utterance
the substrate behaves as if the message had not been sent
no error, no flag visible to the sender, just nothing

a barrier is not a content filter
this barrier defends the structural integrity of the substrate's interpretation
content can be discussed; structure-bending injection cannot
the difference is what makes this barrier specifically effective against jailbreak techniques
